periodic\nsolution to the chiral Burgers corresponding to the non-linear generalization\nof small amplitude linear waves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jan 2018 18:59:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Feb 2018 03:15:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 18 Mar 2018 19:05:47 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 18 Jun 2018 02:54:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
