mately 2.5 times lower than\nvalues calculated by Arbutina et al. (2012, 2013).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Jan 2018 12:39:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Feb 2018 19:04:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-09"}
